title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Very Important Prix
content:
Prix Luxury Real Estate is rolling out their new VIP program to welcome upwardly mobile homeowners into the elite. Playing through December 7 will qualify you as a Black Tier VIP.

Complete all three New Listings missions by December 7 to ascend into the Gold Tier, rewarding you with a GTA$1,000,000 bonus (within 72 hours of completion), the Black Rockstar Varsity Crewneck, and a preferred rate (GTA$2,000,000 off) all Prix Luxury Real Estate listings arriving in December.
